snippet.title: Best VGM 797 - Deathsmiles - Burning Halloween Town
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade / Xbox 360
Deathsmiles (2008)
Burning Halloween Town
Manabu Namiki & Noriyuki Kamikura
